properties.name: Crux Deluxe
properties.description:
This week, we are putting the x back in x-mas, in an unorthodox, quixotic excursion to examine the various cruxes, quincunxes and confluxes that the city has to offer. Please excuse us if this all seems too perplexing or inexpedient. If you fedex some spandex to the pontifex, maybe he can join us at the apex.
